				<div class="feature col-6">

					<div class="list-group">
						<h2>STEP-03: Now Accept VC from Mobile</h2>
						<p>Once you successfully receive the VC in your mobile, you need to open it and click "Accept" button.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="feature col-6">

					<div class="list-group">
						<h2>STEP-04: Send Proof Request</h2>
						<p>Once you successfully stored the VC, you can proof your role as "student" of Faber College</p>
						<div>
							<a href="/proofReq" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-primary">Request Proof</a>

